---
title: Mushroom Spaghetti Bolognese with Parmesan & Pear Salad
description: Vegetarians can still get a rich, hearty and satisfying bowl of pasta with this bolognese based on delicious mushrooms. Cook up the chunky, veggie-packed sauce then toss it through perfectly ‘al dente’ pasta for an Italian feast that will make you cry “Bravo”!
